Sie können ihn vor oder neben dem Sofa, im Arbeitszimmer, auf dem Balkon usw. aufstellen. ✔ Zuverlässige Qualität: Der runde Tisch besteht aus MDF und Kunststoff, die Schubladen aus Tannenholz und sorgen so für gute Stabilität und chemische Beständigkeit. Glastischplatten und glatte MDF-Tischplatten sind leicht zu pflegen und zu reinigen. ✔ Großer Stauraum: Das 2 teilige Couchtisch-Set ist mit zwei Schubladen und zwei Arbeitsflächen ausgestattet, so bekommt man einen großen Stauraum und ein gewisses Maß an Privatsphäre.

[Spacious Workstation] Who's ready for Spring? Get a little bit of inspiration for the coming season from this farmhouse garden potting bench. Made of 100% fir wood, this table is sturdy enough for outdoor using with its 46.8x18.5inch workstation. Compared with other potting bench, its surface is spacious for putting many tools or planters from your loved garden. [4 Ample Storage Shelves] If you are a big fan of gardening, this potting bench will be a great choice. With 65" total height and 36" potting height, 4 ample storage shelves are designed to keep your tools handy and in one place without bending over or squatting. Constructed with 1 upper shelf including 2 grids and 3 lower shelves, this potting table is ample enough for not only small tools but also extra soil, pots and other gardening supplies. [Splash Plate& Side Hook] There are always many small kits when gardening such as hand trowels, rakes, transplanters, towels, gloves and, of course, your farmer's hats. Just with some nails, the splash plate will become a board to hold your tools. Besides, the potting table comes with 3 hooks in the side which will make gardening easier. [Anti-Falling Safety Device] There is not always flat in the garden. For your safety in setting the potting bench, it is designed with an anti-falling device. There are two anti-falling devices with ground nails which can fix the bench in the ground for better safety. [Dimension] Overall size: 46.9x19.3x65inch(LXWXH). Each Grid: 22.5x10.2inch(LXW); Tabletop: 48x18.5inch(LXW). For more dimensions, please refer to the size image.Please feel free to contact us if any issues.
